{"tid":2444549,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"鄭中基海濱騷車輛套票被掃光  RB演唱會預售秒殺 宣佈加場","createTime":"2021-03-13T01:47:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T01:47:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6636b6604fc3885be1b1b05e2bf309c99d317d57","tid":2444549,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T01:47:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210313/LJL4Z6PV35A3FJF54AT4TLKWDQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210313%2FLJL4Z6PV35A3FJF54AT4TLKWDQ%2F&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI7AecByD1k%2Bs4QbbWwjAUoc%3D&h=c5c79b78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210313%2FLJL4Z6PV35A3FJF54AT4TLKWDQ%2F&h=e2c72945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210313/LJL4Z6PV35A3FJF54AT4TLKWDQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭中基海濱騷車輛套票被掃光 <br />\nRB演唱會預售秒殺 宣佈加場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5RG4r-dZrqnfZVfUIT8GGpteXsU=/640x319/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YN3NAS32QJCV5M2HHPCTZZTVMU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5RG4r-dZrqnfZVfUIT8GGpteXsU%3D%2F640x319%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYN3NAS32QJCV5M2HHPCTZZTVMU.jpg&h=07e92f12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■RubberBand前晚拍片呼籲樂迷買飛，昨日預售甫開始，門票已被秒殺。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n樂隊RubberBand（RB）和鄭中基將在下月分別舉行演唱會，門票同樣在昨日優先預售，反應皆十分熱烈。RB下月４及５日在紅館舉行「RubberBand Ciao 2021」演唱會，門票昨早10點優先預售，但僅僅一分鐘便全部售罄；昨晚RB即宣佈於下月3日加開一場，即合共三場。而鄭中基下月舉行首個drive in演唱會，設有近百套售價6,000元的四人一車套票，雖然有人指售價略貴，但開賣不久亦光速售罄，由此可見樂迷的確「餓」show太久，誓要進行「報復式看演唱會」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「一齊印證時代」<br />\n<br />\n對於門票被秒殺，主音6號昨日回覆《蘋果》表示：「好suprised，好感謝啲朋友樂迷一早10點就上網狂click，我起身後都有回應朋友，一係等到17號公開發售。𠵱家決定開多一場，希望多啲朋友可以嚟感受，今次個騷比起三年前更加有時代印記，三年前係比較自我團隊，但今時今日已好唔同，就喺呢個時代切入點同大家一齊印證。」至於同期的鄭中基演唱會反應同樣熱烈，6號坦言十分開心，以前開騷睇騷是平常不過，但現在卻要經歷起落，祈求疫情不要反覆。加場與另外兩場的門票，將於下周三公開發售。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MxwR8o8Y_JuSJ0_AWQ_IOadNtQU=/640x441/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XELLPTVCYNCD5IA6TDQQXP56WY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMxwR8o8Y_JuSJ0_AWQ_IOadNtQU%3D%2F640x441%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXELLPTVCYNCD5IA6TDQQXP56WY.jpg&h=69e7c181&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鄭中基與經理人昨日上載新片解析演唱會相關事宜，特別提到車輛只限私家車，高度限制在1.65米下。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yj2Q56rgvj1vBQKXNZI3NJL6dh8=/1280x774/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GZA6G2MY4VBQ7L3ZEYPBAPJAGI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fyj2Q56rgvj1vBQKXNZI3NJL6dh8%3D%2F1280x774%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGZA6G2MY4VBQ7L3ZEYPBAPJAGI.jpg&h=c553856c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鄭中基演唱會車輛與座位觀眾將分為兩個區域，入口亦會分開。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n鄭中基下月24至25日於中環海濱舉行「Drive In Ultra - WEE are Ronald Cheng自駕演唱會」，昨日公門票公開發售，車輛套票被掃一空，而座位門票亦僅餘少量。演唱會主辦發言人Kenny昨日回覆《蘋果》時表示，之前已有不少super car，如法拉利及林寶堅尼等的車會也問及售票情況，因此他相信屆時會有不少此類車的車主捧場。Kenny同時表示入場的車輛全部皆會檢查人數，以及給名牌識別，以防有人偷運其他人入場，他謂：「其實有人問點解唔做全場都係坐車睇騷，但計過場地只可容納500架車，維持唔到成本，因製作費都過千萬，同埋我哋唔想只有車嘅人先可以睇。」鄭中基的YouTube頻道昨日也有上載短片，解答今次個唱疑問。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/C5O1dUAqOi7LA4HfvIUr5df11_c=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QHIYS3O6RVHAREFTWEXJS2W3WE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FC5O1dUAqOi7LA4HfvIUr5df11_c%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQHIYS3O6RVHAREFTWEXJS2W3WE.jpg&h=3e02b901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林二汶積極備戰<br />\n<br />\n除了RB及鄭中基外，林二汶和梁嘉茵（Serrini）亦將在本月底及下月在紅館及旺角麥花臣場館開騷，兩人的門票同樣售罄，而林二汶近日積極備戰，前晚她在社交網貼出跟樂隊合照，當中何韻詩胞兄何秉舜出任音樂總監，網民大呼期待。"}]}